title: Skyman Android
description:
Playerthree is launching a game on behalf of Legal and General.
Put on your jump suit, check your equipment and prepare for launch. 
Play as our stuntman and try to earn a living being launched across the sky, the aim to finish a jump season in tact and with as much money in the bank as possible.
Easy to pick up and play with simple but fun one-touch controls 
Use your in-game earnings to buy and upgrade power ups to help you jump higher and further 

Protect your earnings to help you finish with a high score 
Compete against friends, family and the rest of the world on our high score leader board 

100% free, no hidden in-game charges 
Can you unlock all achievements?
Requires Android: 1.5 AND UP
